  "text": "In the case presented in Fig. 4 [CITATION_1] defined these ranges as follows: Cluster 1: 30-40 dBu, Cluster 2: 40-60 dBu, and Cluster 3: 60-70 dBu (the detailed description of designations of clusters from cited literature can be found above in this section). Considering a fact that the typical AE response depends on many experimental parameters, materials characteristics, and used measurement equipment, and a fact that some of them have stochastic nature it was decided to re-evaluate cluster boundaries based on statistical analysis of AE data. ",
